<li>Best Cinematographer, Kim Hyung-goo</li>
<li>Best Visual Effects: <a href="/wiki/The_Orphanage_(company)" title="The Orphanage (company)">The Orphanage</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><b><a href="/w/index.php?title=Asia-Pacific_Film_Festivals&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Asia-Pacific Film Festivals (page does not exist)">Asia-Pacific Film Festivals</a></b>
<ul>
<li>Best Editing, Seon Min Kim</li>
<li>Best Sound, Tae-young Choi</li>
<li>Best Supporting Actor, Hie-bong Byeon</li>
</ul>
